Title: Buffalo Woodcut
Type: print
Media: kitakata, wenzhou, ink
Size: 30cm x 23cm
Tags: relief print, woodcut, big five
Date: 2026
-----

This was carved from a piece of plywood using Flexcut and Pfeil tools.
I used the vintage [Columbian press](https://swanseaprintworkshop.org.uk/what-we-do/relief-press/) at the Swansea Print workshop. What a privilege to use a machine with such history, and still in perfect working order.

I've printed it on kitakata and Wenzhou paper. I am drawn to the delicate but strong texture of the Wenzhou paper. It's translucent, as you can see in the video.

